Page[133]=new Array("The following XML fragment shows the elements used to create the rows in the Sample Collection itemset on the Dose VS2 form.","The Repeating Data itemset contains two rows with predefined values:","Hour 10, Minute 0","Hour 10, Minute 2 ","The value of 50.000 is entered for the Hour 10, Minute 0 data point.","&lt;PATIENTDATA PATIENTINITIALS=&#8216;RDF&#8217; SITEMNEMONIC=&#8216;01&#8217; FORMSETREFNAME=&#8216;CommonCRF&#8217; FORMREFNAME=&#8216;frmDOSEVS2&#8217; FORMINDEX=&#8216;0&#8217; ","SECTIONNAME=&#8216;sctSampleCollection&#8217; ITEMSETNAME=&#8216;sctSampleCollection&#8217;&gt;","&lt;DATA TAG=&#8216;sctSampleCollection.sctSampleCollection.itmTime.itmTime&#8217; ITEMSETINDEX=&#8216;1&#8217; HOUR='10' MINUTE='0' /&gt;","&lt;DATA TAG=&#8216;sctSampleCollection.sctSampleCollection.itmMeasurement.itmMeasurement&#8217; ITEMSETINDEX=&#8216;1&#8217; VALUE='50.00' /&gt;","&lt;DATA TAG=&#8216;sctSampleCollection.sctSampleCollection.itmTime.itmTime&#8217; ITEMSETINDEX=&#8216;2&#8217; HOUR='10' MINUTE='2' /&gt;","&lt;/PATIENTDATA&gt;","Example: Creating rows for a Repeating Data itemset","180380.htm");
